<div id="team">
  <div class="centered">
    <h4>Modern Day Artisans</h4>
    <h5>meet the team</h5>

    <div class="split vertical">
      <div class="orange left">
        <h3>Symonds (Steve)</h3>
        <h4>Co-Founder, VP of Sales</h4>
        <p>
          Steve is a serial entrepreneur, experienced in building digital media, social media, mobile and high tech companies in a variety of verticals. Steve has propelled numerous early-stage companies through development of market-leading products and services, leveraging IP rights, and raising capital.
        </p>
        <div class="email">
          <%= tag(:img, src: 'img/mail-icon.png', height: 10, width: 14) %>
          <a href="mailto:steve@symondsandson.com">steve@symondsandson.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right white">
        <%= tag(:img, src: 'img/josh-symonds.jpg', alt: 'Josh Symonds', id: 'josh') %>
        <h3>Son (Josh)</h3>
        <h4>Co-Founder, Lead Developer</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="careers">
  <h3>Careers</h3>
  <div class="black split vertical centered">
    <div class="left">
      <p>Do you have amazing skills, but feel you're undercompensated? Are you a meticulous, friendly, personable and responsible coder who works well in a team? Would you like to work remotely and still be an integral part of our projects? If you have many of the skills we need, here's your chance:</p>
      <p>If you're interested please provide a copy of your resume and cover letter. Include your GitHub account, StackOverflow profile, or whatever other information you have that would establish your credentials as a great coder and fine human being.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="right">
      <p>We're hiring developers experienced in&hellip;</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Ruby and Ruby on Rails</li>
        <li>Angular.js and/or Ember.js</li>
        <li>Elasticsearch</li>
        <li>Sidekiq, Resque, or other Redis backed delayed job system</li>
        <li>DevOps (Chef preferred)</li>
        <li>Working Remotely</li>
      </ul>
      <div id="join-the-team" class="bordered">Join The Team</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="blog">
  <div class="centered">
    <h3>We're Not Just Developers</h3>
    <h4>We're thought leaders of our craft.</h4>
    <div id="quill-divider">
      <span class="line left"></span>
      <span class="line right"></span>
            <%= tag(:img, src: 'img/blog-icon.png') %>
    </div>
    <br/>
    <div id="posts">
      <% data.blog.posts.each do |post| %>
        <div class="post">
          <div class="title"><%= post.title %></div>
          <div class="lede"><%= post.lede %></div>
          <div class="link"><a href=<%= post.url %>>Read More</a></div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id='have_a_project' class='centered'>
  <h2>Have a Project?</h2>
  <p>We'd love to hear the details.</p>
  <form action="https://symondsandson-contact.herokuapp.com/contact" method="post" id='contact_form'>
    <div class='column'>
      <label>Name <span class='required'>*</span></label>
      <input type='text' name='name' class='required' />

      <label>Phone</label>
      <input type='text' name='phone' />

      <label>Deadline</label>
      <input type='text' name='deadline' />

      <label>Budget</label>
      <input type='text' name='budget' />

      <input class="button" name="send" type="submit" value="Send">
    </div>
    <div class='column'>
      <label>Email <span class='required'>*</span></label>
      <input type='email' name='email' class='required email' />

      <label>Brief Description <span class='required'>*</span></label>
      <textarea name='description' class='required'></textarea>

      <div class='explanation'><span class='required'>*</span> denotes required fields</div>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>

<footer>
  <div class='centered'>
    &copy; 2013 Symonds &amp; Son
  </div>
</footer>
